    public class SupportMapFragmentActivity
extends androidx.appcompat.app.AppCompatActivity
implements MapFragment.OnMapViewReadyCallback, OnMapReadyCallback, MapView.OnDidFinishRenderingFrameListener
    Test activity showcasing using the MapFragment API using Support Library Fragments.

    Uses MapboxMapOptions to initialise the Fragment.
